Port Scan
Attack Type: Hack
Effect: Causes a targeted enemy to take 5 + DamageBonus% more damage
Flavour Text: “Knock knock… oh wow, you really don’t use a firewall, huh?”
Combat Formula: DamageBonus% = 5 + (LevelDiff × 2)

